             was indicted for <rs id="t17770409-49-off243" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17770409-49-off243" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770409-49-off243" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a silver watch, value 40 s. a steal watch chain, value 2 d. a steal seal, value 1 d. and a brass watch key, value 1 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17770409-49-victim459" type="victimName">
                     James
                      Christie
                  <interp inst="t17770409-49-victim459" type="surname" value="Christie"></interp>
